00:26:32,680 --> 00:26:36,840
I do think that there could have been at the beginning, an idea that somebody could have said,

321
00:26:36,840 --> 00:26:40,520
this is a respiratory virus, it has many overlapping symptoms with common colds and

322
00:26:40,520 --> 00:26:45,720
flus. You should think about this in your patients. And we are going to allow testing to be done,

323
00:26:45,720 --> 00:26:50,120
if you have certain risk factors for this, and they shouldn't just be restricted to you having

