00:27:44,040 --> 00:27:48,760
that type of emergency response ready five years from now when people have long forgotten about

336
00:27:48,840 --> 00:27:52,920
this? I hope so. I think this is something that's going to leave a mark on society. This

337
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:58,200
hasn't happened in modern times, not during the 68 or 57 pandemics. And it did happen in 1918,

338
00:27:58,200 --> 00:28:02,600
but that's not in anybody's living memory anymore. So I do think that this is something that people

339
00:28:02,600 --> 00:28:06,760
will remember. And they will remember the costs that they personally had to incur filing for

340
00:28:06,760 --> 00:28:12,600
unemployment for the first time. All of that type of stuff is going to hopefully push the public to

341
00:28:12,600 --> 00:28:16,760
demand that pandemic preparedness be taken seriously. So this doesn't happen again,

342
00:28:16,760 --> 00:28:20,920
and that this should be a priority. This should be something that's in a candidate's campaign

