00:28:24,360 --> 00:28:29,240
But we've gone through this cycle for a long, long time. You can think about anthrax in 2001,

345
00:28:29,240 --> 00:28:37,720
bird flu scares in 2005, the H1N1 pandemic in 2009, Ebola in 2013, 2014, Zika, right after that.

346
00:28:37,720 --> 00:28:43,240
We've had multiple types of episodes, and you get this cycle where everybody runs to fund this

