00:29:39,240 --> 00:29:44,200
over again. Yeah, I do suspect we're going to have many more deaths, probably closer to that 60,000.

360
00:29:44,760 --> 00:29:49,720
I do think that the fact that this outbreak touched people personally in a way that Ebola did not,

361
00:29:49,720 --> 00:29:54,520
the way that Zika did not, the way even that H1N1 did not, H1N1 actually engendered complacency

362
00:29:54,520 --> 00:30:00,120
because only about 12,000 Americans died. And then people said we all overreacted to H1N1. So I

